sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Buyer
    actor Seller
    participant Kong as Kong Gateway
    participant Transfer as Transfer Orchestrator
    participant TransferSvc as Transfer Service
    participant OTP as OTP Wrapper
    participant OutSys as OutSystems Credit API
    participant Ledger as Credit Transaction Service
    participant Ticket as Ticket Service
    participant Market as Marketplace Service

    Buyer->>Kong: POST /transfer/initiate
    Kong->>Transfer: listingId
    Transfer->>TransferSvc: create transfer
    TransferSvc-->>Transfer: pending_seller_acceptance
    Transfer-->>Seller: async notify request exists

    Seller->>Kong: POST /transfer/{id}/seller-accept
    Kong->>Transfer: seller accepts
    Transfer->>OTP: send buyer OTP
    OTP-->>Transfer: buyerVerificationSid
    Transfer->>TransferSvc: set pending_buyer_otp

    Buyer->>Kong: POST /transfer/{id}/buyer-verify
    Kong->>Transfer: buyer OTP
    Transfer->>OTP: verify buyer OTP
    OTP-->>Transfer: verified
    Transfer->>OTP: send seller OTP
    OTP-->>Transfer: sellerVerificationSid
    Transfer->>TransferSvc: set pending_seller_otp

    Seller->>Kong: POST /transfer/{id}/seller-verify
    Kong->>Transfer: seller OTP
    Transfer->>OTP: verify seller OTP
    OTP-->>Transfer: verified
    Transfer->>OutSys: deduct buyer and credit seller
    Transfer->>Ledger: log buyer and seller credit records
    Transfer->>Ticket: transfer ticket ownership
    Transfer->>Market: mark listing completed
    Transfer->>TransferSvc: mark transfer completed
    Transfer-->>Buyer: success
    Transfer-->>Seller: success
